Diamonds

Ahmet Tuncel

30 Kasm 2017

Library Loading

library(tidyverse)
library(ggthemes)

Data Loading and splittin Test Traing Data

diamonds_test <- diamonds %>% mutate(diamond_id = row_number()) %>% 
  group_by(cut, color, clarity) %>% sample_frac(0.2) %>% ungroup()

diamonds_train <- anti_join(diamonds %>% mutate(diamond_id = row_number()), 
                            diamonds_test, by = "diamond_id")

Plot Geom Point

ggplot(diamonds,aes(carat,price,
                    color=clarity,size=price))+geom_point()+
  xlab("carat")+ylab("price")+
  ggtitle("carat X price ve size")

Plot Histogram

df<-ggplot(diamonds)
ah<-aes(x=price,colour=cut)
gst<-geom_histogram(bins= 200)
tit<-("diamonds clarity X carat")
df+ah+gst+ggtitle(tit)

Plot BoxPlot

bx<-aes(clarity, carat)
tit<-("clarity X carat")
gx<-geom_boxplot()
df+bx+gx+ggtitle(tit)+ylab("Log10 Carat")

Plot Geom Bar

br<-aes(x=clarity,y=price)
br<-aes(x=clarity,y=price,fill=cut)
tit<-("clarity X price")
gbd<-geom_bar(stat="identity",position="dodge")
df+br+gbd+ggtitle(tit)+coord_flip()

Plot Boxplo

bx<-aes(clarity, carat)

tit<-("diamonds clarity X carat")

gx<-geom_boxplot()

tg <-theme_igray()

df+bx+gx+ggtitle(tit)+ylab("Log10 Carat")+tg

Linear Regression and Prediction

regressor = lm(formula = price ~ .,
               data = diamonds_train)
